This map is just a BETA. I will texture and add lighting on the FINAL release, so please dont let these effect your rating. This is my FIRST released map, so give me a break :D.

The Map includes many obsticles to get by, with a few secrets, and a fun zone on completion of the map.

Your welcome to put this on your servers, if so, leave the ip and ill come have a look :)
